even exist anymore?

313
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:03,220
I just want to save my dad.

314
00:19:05,110 --> 00:19:05,730
Ms. Zhang,

315
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:08,290
please help me.

316
00:19:11,550 --> 00:19:12,050
Wan Chao,

317
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:14,570
where are you right now? Are you safe?

318
00:19:15,590 --> 00:19:16,290
