319
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:18,420
The local police put out
a warrant on me.

320
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:19,700
I can't leave.

321
00:19:20,640 --> 00:19:21,090
Listen,

322
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:23,860
I'll give you a number.

323
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:25,380
Contact her.

324
00:19:30,030 --> 00:19:30,490
Sir,

325
00:19:30,830 --> 00:19:31,700
can I ask you about someone?

326
00:19:32,070 --> 00:19:32,900
Have you seen this person?

327
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:33,770
No.

328
00:19:37,240 --> 00:19:38,570
Ma'am, is there a back door?

329
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:19,440
[As one of the lead prosecutors,
I was too eager for results…]

330
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:26,250
Mishandling a case

331
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:28,530
entails lifelong accountability.

332
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:31,770
Remember, Hong Liang,

333
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:34,180
compared to the long-term social

334
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:37,140
and legal impact of a wrongful case,

335
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:39,090
the consequences of personal mistakes

336
00:20:39,350 --> 00:20:40,660
are insignificant.

337
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:51,760
[As one of the lead prosecutors,
I was too focused on redefining the case…]

338
00:20:55,030 --> 00:20:55,380
Hong Liang.

339
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:56,330
Ms. Zheng.

340
00:20:57,270 --> 00:20:57,700
Han,

341
00:20:58,110 --> 00:20:59,050
would you give us a minute?

342
00:20:59,510 --> 00:21:01,010
I need to speak with Mr. Hong privately.

343
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:03,090
Thanks.

344
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:05,620
Hong Liang.

345
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:09,700
It's been days since we talked.

346
00:21:12,550 --> 00:21:13,180
The time's come.

347
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:15,900
We need to put together a report

348
00:21:16,790 --> 00:21:17,570
and get Mr. Zhang's go-ahead

349
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:19,140
to set up an investigation group.

350
00:21:21,350 --> 00:21:21,900
It is

351
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:24,090
an investigation group,
not a Guidance Group.

352
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:26,770
Why an investigation group?

353
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:28,660
Don't play dumb.
Haven't you seen the news?

354
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:29,460
Just write what I say.

355
00:21:33,030 --> 00:21:33,730
Dear

356
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:34,900
Mr. Zhang,

357
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:36,330
in view of

358
00:21:36,480 --> 00:21:39,090
the serious accident at Wanchuan Mining

359
00:21:39,350 --> 00:21:39,980
and its major impact...

360
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:40,530
Accident

361
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:42,810
at Wanchuan Mining?

362
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:44,220
Hong Liang, you really don't know?

363
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:47,220
You haven't seen any news?

364
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:49,570
What have you even
been doing this whole time?

365
00:21:50,310 --> 00:21:51,730
How are you completely
out of the loop on something this big?

366
00:22:00,350 --> 00:22:01,380
How many casualties?

367
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:03,010
Two dead, thirteen injured.

368
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:04,530
Six are in critical condition.

369
00:22:05,550 --> 00:22:06,290
I don't think

370
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,940
this was just some safety mishap.

371
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:11,460
They'll call it that

372
00:22:11,480 --> 00:22:12,570
at the press conference,

373
00:22:12,590 --> 00:22:13,290
but I don't buy it.

374
00:22:13,550 --> 00:22:14,900
That's why we need Mr. Zhang

375
00:22:15,350 --> 00:22:16,290
to set up an investigation group.

376
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:18,490
I can't let it go
until the truth comes out,

377
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:20,770
or I wouldn't be doing my job.

378
00:22:22,790 --> 00:22:23,090
Come on,

379
00:22:23,590 --> 00:22:24,050
keep writing.

380
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:29,860
Regarding the mine disaster...

381
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:30,380
Regarding

382
00:22:31,830 --> 00:22:32,620
the mine disaster...

383
00:22:34,350 --> 00:22:36,620
Shouldn't we wait for
Dongping's officials

384
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:38,180
to announce something

385
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:39,290
before stepping in?

386
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:40,380
Hong Liang,

387
00:22:42,310 --> 00:22:43,980
remember how we used to

388
00:22:44,790 --> 00:22:45,810
take bold guesses

389
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:48,090
during case work?

390
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:01,530
Can we really trust them?

391
00:23:02,480 --> 00:23:04,140
We wait for their findings, seriously?

392
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:06,810
Come on.

393
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:09,620
Regarding the mine disaster...

394
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:10,810
Regarding the mine disaster...

395
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:13,620
I mean, I'm not even sure

396
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:15,530
I'm the right person for this.

397
00:23:16,510 --> 00:23:18,530
The only reason

398
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:21,140
I joined the Guidance Group

399
00:23:22,350 --> 00:23:24,010
is someone tipped us off

400
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:25,570
about duty-related crimes in Dongping,

401
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:28,460
some protectors shielding criminals.

402
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:30,620
It'd be awkward if I showed up now.

403
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:32,140
Hong Liang,

404
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,860
we both know

405
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:37,420
what's really going on in Dongping.

406
00:23:38,270 --> 00:23:40,010
They broke up the old Guidance Group,

407
00:23:40,310 --> 00:23:41,380
and now there's a mine disaster.

408
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:42,420
Are you telling me

409
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:45,330
there's no duty-related crime

410
00:23:45,350 --> 00:23:46,620
or protection here in Dongping?

411
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:49,940
Keep writing.

412
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:52,090
Regarding the mine disaster...

413
00:23:52,110 --> 00:23:53,090
Regarding my kid...

414
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,490
Look at me!

415
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:57,570
I mean,

416
00:23:59,590 --> 00:24:00,180
my wife

417
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:01,940
kept me up last night,

418
00:24:02,030 --> 00:24:03,250
stressing about

419
00:24:03,270 --> 00:24:04,420
our kid's education—

420
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,940
telling me, "Liang,
as a father, aren't you concerned?"

421
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:07,420
Hong Liang,

422
00:24:09,590 --> 00:24:10,660
you haven't done with your job, right?

423
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,010
No.

424
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,460
Then act like it.

425
00:24:16,030 --> 00:24:17,330
My health is shot.

426
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:19,660
Lately, I don't know why,

427
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:21,090
I can't sleep at all.

428
00:24:21,270 --> 00:24:22,330
What are you getting at?

429
00:24:24,350 --> 00:24:26,140
Remember what you promised
before we left Dongping?

430
00:24:27,750 --> 00:24:29,620
If things ever turned around here,

431
00:24:30,550 --> 00:24:31,860
you'd come back to help, uniform or not,

432
00:24:32,590 --> 00:24:34,090
wherever, whenever, no questions asked.

433
00:24:34,110 --> 00:24:34,980
Am I wrong?

434
00:24:37,640 --> 00:24:38,380
Changed your mind now?

435
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:39,900
You don't want to step up,

436
00:24:40,110 --> 00:24:41,290
or is it just fear?

437
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:43,810
Hong Liang,

438
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:45,380
people died.

439
00:24:46,830 --> 00:24:48,010
People died in Dongping.

440
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:48,860
Wanchuan Mining...

441
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:50,770
I can't go there!

442
00:24:52,830 --> 00:24:53,620
Why not?

443
00:25:05,350 --> 00:25:06,180
Who do you think

444
00:25:07,310 --> 00:25:08,010
actually runs Wanchuan Mining?

445
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:09,940
Wan Hai, right?

446
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:12,810
Prisoner or not,

447
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:15,090
that guy's still the owner.

448
00:25:15,310 --> 00:25:17,660
So whatever happens at the mine now

449
00:25:17,790 --> 00:25:20,810
could tie right back
to the Wan Hai case.

450
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:21,980
That case is ironclad!

451
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:22,730
Hang on.

452
00:25:26,350 --> 00:25:26,860
Ironclad?

453
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:30,570
Hong Liang,

454
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:34,380
now you're seeing

455
00:25:35,110 --> 00:25:37,010
the Wan Hai case as ironclad?

456
00:25:38,590 --> 00:25:39,180
Well,

457
00:25:43,270 --> 00:25:45,330
I guess I read you right from day one.

458
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:47,330
I've never misjudged anyone.

459
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:48,730
You're a coward.

460
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:50,620
You really are.

461
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:55,980
Honestly, I'm disappointed.

462
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:03,770
But thank you, anyway,

463
00:26:04,880 --> 00:26:06,380
for your work on the case analysis

464
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:09,380
back in Dongping.

465
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:11,770
Thanks.

466
00:27:38,270 --> 00:27:38,700
ID, please.

467
00:27:40,270 --> 00:27:41,530
Do me a favor, please.

468
00:27:43,510 --> 00:27:44,090
Need to borrow your phone.

469
00:27:58,110 --> 00:27:58,420
Hello?

470
00:27:59,070 --> 00:28:00,010
Ms. Zheng Yaping?

471
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:01,810
Yes.

472
00:28:02,110 --> 00:28:02,860
This is Wan Chao.

473
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:04,810
I'm Wan Hai's son.

474
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:07,700
Can I have your email address?

475
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:09,900
I want to send you something.

476
00:28:12,030 --> 00:28:12,660
Please write it down.

477
00:28:40,840 --> 00:28:46,200
[Self-review on Major Mistakes Made while
Handling the Wanchuan Mining Shooting]

478
00:29:32,790 --> 00:29:33,420
Hong Liang,

479
00:29:34,270 --> 00:29:35,010
we appreciate your hard work.

480
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:37,770
Let's hear what you've got.

481
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:39,770
As soon as I got to Dongping,

482
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:42,570
I went straight to Yongqing River

483
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:45,730
where Qiao Zhenxing's body was found.

484
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:48,860
I thought about getting
another water sample,

485
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:51,700
but my wife, a lab tech,

486
00:29:53,270 --> 00:29:54,090
told me

487
00:29:54,310 --> 00:29:55,180
the season's changed,

488
00:29:55,550 --> 00:29:56,420
the ice's melted,

489
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:58,460
and the riverbank ecosystem
is different now.

490
00:29:59,310 --> 00:30:00,380
So even if I took a new sample,

491
00:30:01,160 --> 00:30:02,090
it wouldn't mean much.

492
00:30:03,750 --> 00:30:04,660
So, sirs,

493
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:06,090
if you would like

494
00:30:06,270 --> 00:30:08,330
this case to progress,

495
00:30:09,310 --> 00:30:10,620
you might need to

496
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:13,460
provide the test report

497
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:14,490
of the Zhongxing Road water sample

498
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:16,940
to whoever

499
00:30:18,590 --> 00:30:19,620
takes over in the future.

500
00:30:20,110 --> 00:30:20,940
That's all I've got.

501
00:30:26,550 --> 00:30:27,010
Hong Liang,

502
00:30:29,030 --> 00:30:31,250
you pushed for a formal investigation

503
00:30:31,270 --> 00:30:32,420
into Qiao Zhenxing's case, right?

504
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:35,090
We gave you green light

505
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:36,730
because the higher-ups

506
00:30:36,750 --> 00:30:38,090
also had suspicions about what happened.

507
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:39,460
Before you left,

508
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:41,900
I handed you Qiao's bank details,

509
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:42,980
statements,

510
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:44,730
and call logs.

511
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:46,460
And now, after all this,

512
00:30:47,110 --> 00:30:47,810
is the water sample

513
00:30:48,920 --> 00:30:49,980
all you've got?

514
00:30:52,310 --> 00:30:53,460
You called me

515
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:55,700
late at night about a thesis.

516
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:56,980
Were you actually working the case,

517
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,330
or writing someone's thesis?

518
00:31:30,270 --> 00:31:30,660
Come in.

519
00:31:35,790 --> 00:31:36,530
Commissioner Sun is here too?

520
00:31:37,590 --> 00:31:37,980
Mr. Zhang.

521
00:31:38,550 --> 00:31:39,140
This is urgent.

522
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:40,330
Go ahead.

523
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:41,900
I'll step out.

524
00:31:42,110 --> 00:31:42,490
Hold on.

525
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:44,050
You should see this too.

526
00:31:54,640 --> 00:31:55,140
This man

527
00:31:55,510 --> 00:31:57,050
is Jiang Hongjun,

528
00:31:57,070 --> 00:31:58,570
chief at
Dongping Development Zone sub-bureau.

529
00:32:01,070 --> 00:32:02,090
Who sent you this video?

530
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:03,700
Wan Hai's son,

531
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:04,860
Wan Chao.

532
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:20,490
Ms. Zheng,

533
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:23,980
