534
00:32:24,310 --> 00:32:25,090
He said

535
00:32:25,310 --> 00:32:27,050
Zhang Wenjing gave him my number

536
00:32:27,350 --> 00:32:28,730
and told him

537
00:32:29,070 --> 00:32:30,140
to report it to the provincial office.

538
00:32:42,590 --> 00:32:43,050
Mr. Zhang,

539
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:44,220
Commissioner Sun,

540
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:46,530
based on the evidence

541
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:47,380
and report materials

542
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:48,570
we've got so far,

543
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:49,660
I recommend

544
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:51,180
we send a special task force

545
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:52,620
to Dongping immediately.

546
00:32:56,030 --> 00:32:56,490
Xiangqun,

547
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:59,530
seems Yaping was right on the money.

548
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:00,770
I'll report it

549
00:33:01,480 --> 00:33:02,050
to Mr. Yan

550
00:33:02,590 --> 00:33:03,570
right away.

551
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:05,460
Commissioner Sun,

552
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:07,570
should the Eleventh Division

553
00:33:08,070 --> 00:33:09,090
take the lead

554
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:10,810
on this task force?

555
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:11,330
Absolutely.

556
00:33:12,310 --> 00:33:12,700
Mr. Zhang.

557
00:33:12,920 --> 00:33:13,770
I'll call a meeting right away

558
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:15,900
and pick our best team for the job.

559
00:33:16,070 --> 00:33:16,420
Perfect.

560
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:17,090
Mr. Zhang.

561
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:21,050
Did you sign off on Hong's resignation?

562
00:33:23,480 --> 00:33:23,860
Yes.

563
00:33:25,590 --> 00:33:26,770
It's already processing.

564
00:33:30,110 --> 00:33:30,730
Yaping,

565
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,620
let us know if you have any suggestions.

566
00:33:35,510 --> 00:33:36,460
We're on a tight deadline,

567
00:33:37,160 --> 00:33:38,250
can we keep

568
00:33:38,550 --> 00:33:40,420
the old Guidance Group in place?

569
00:33:41,310 --> 00:33:42,730
That's a good plan.

570
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:43,810
I agree.

571
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:44,810
Hong Liang,

572
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:47,220
while we're at it,

573
00:33:47,750 --> 00:33:48,810
let's also reexamine

574
00:33:49,200 --> 00:33:49,940
the Qiao Zhenxing case

575
00:33:50,790 --> 00:33:51,530
from square one.

576
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:53,420
I have a feeling

577
00:33:53,830 --> 00:33:54,860
the two cases are linked.

578
00:33:56,750 --> 00:33:57,530
I'll get started, then.

579
00:33:57,640 --> 00:33:57,980
Good.

580
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:06,250
Hong Liang!

581
00:34:08,710 --> 00:34:09,570
What were you fumbling with?

582
00:34:23,190 --> 00:34:25,050
The commissioner's tough talk

583
00:34:25,880 --> 00:34:26,690
