Well,

588
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:41,740
guess I'll have to redeem myself.

589
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:51,780
Who told you to do this?!

590
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:53,260
Look around,

591
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:56,050
the mine disaster is all over the news!

592
00:34:56,510 --> 00:34:56,820
You...

593
00:34:57,230 --> 00:34:58,530
Are you trying to make sure

594
00:34:58,550 --> 00:34:59,570
everyone knows?

595
00:35:00,760 --> 00:35:01,260
Mr. Yu,

596
00:35:02,110 --> 00:35:02,780
don't worry.

597
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:05,210
I've got everything
under control from here.

598
00:35:06,590 --> 00:35:07,780
No way I'm giving up this mine.

599
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:08,610
Believe it or not,

600
00:35:08,630 --> 00:35:09,940
one phone call
and I could have you locked up!

601
00:35:10,030 --> 00:35:10,490
Go ahead.

602
00:35:10,670 --> 00:35:11,260
But if I go down,

603
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,490
let's see who I take with me.

604
00:35:13,190 --> 00:35:15,050
Don't act like you're in the clear.

605
00:35:15,190 --> 00:35:16,170
Idiot, you should've

606
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:17,900
stuck to raising pigs and digging coal!

607
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:19,460
Do you even know what new energy is?

608
00:35:19,510 --> 00:35:21,820
Think just owning a mine
and a plot of land

609
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:23,300
means you can sit back and count money?

610
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:24,050
Jiang,

611
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,690
I've risked everything

612
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:26,420
for this mine!

613
00:35:26,550 --> 00:35:27,090
You know what...

614
00:35:27,190 --> 00:35:28,210
Risked everything?

615
00:35:28,230 --> 00:35:29,130
Who do you think you are?

616
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:29,900
Enough!

617
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:30,340
Mr. Yu!

618
00:35:30,670 --> 00:35:31,380
Was I wrong?

619
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:34,490
Have you forgotten who chased you
out of Dongping back then?

620
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:08,130
Mr. Yu,

621
00:36:10,230 --> 00:36:10,900
I wore

622
00:36:12,190 --> 00:36:14,010
mourning clothes at your wife's funeral.

623
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:41,690
You never once

624
00:36:42,710 --> 00:36:43,820
hit me my whole life,

625
00:36:44,920 --> 00:36:46,490
but now you slap me in front of him?

626
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:51,210
You're only
embarrassing yourself, you know?

627
00:36:51,590 --> 00:36:52,130
Listen,

628
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:54,300
you're out

629
00:36:55,190 --> 00:36:55,940
from now on.

630
00:36:56,190 --> 00:36:56,820
No more mine,

631
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:57,740
no more land.

632
00:36:57,960 --> 00:36:58,900
I'm in charge.

633
00:36:59,400 --> 00:36:59,860
Got it?

634
00:37:01,710 --> 00:37:02,820
Mr. Yu, answer me.

635
00:37:05,670 --> 00:37:06,900
If I hadn't done this,

636
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:11,610
would you have just tossed me aside

637
00:37:14,670 --> 00:37:16,170
once all the dirty work was finished?

638
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:25,260
You...

639
00:37:26,110 --> 00:37:27,050
You're out of your mind!

640
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:29,090
So you all get to walk away clean,

641
00:37:34,440 --> 00:37:35,380
and we're left,

642
00:37:36,710 --> 00:37:37,820
doing all your dirty work?

643
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:39,210
Mr. Yu,

644
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:41,010
is that all I've ever been to you?

645
00:37:42,590 --> 00:37:44,380
A coal washer?

646
00:37:46,150 --> 00:37:46,780
Long,

647
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:49,460
what are you saying?

648
00:37:51,150 --> 00:37:52,380
What is this supposed to mean?

649
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,010
I'm telling you right now,

650
00:37:54,710 --> 00:37:55,130
Mr. Yu,

651
00:37:58,840 --> 00:38:00,780
I'm taking the mine and the land.

652
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:02,860
No one's stopping me.

653
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:56,170
Come on.

654
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:57,340
Step over.

655
00:38:58,440 --> 00:39:00,170
Over the brazier, here is the good luck.

656
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:03,130
Mr. Yu wanted me to set this up for me.

657
00:39:03,550 --> 00:39:05,340
A little welcome home ritual
to chase the bad luck away.

658
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:12,570
What's wrong?

659
00:39:15,190 --> 00:39:17,010
A year inside
and you forget how to talk?

660
00:39:18,920 --> 00:39:19,650
Listen,

661
00:39:21,190 --> 00:39:23,380
it's been a big year for us.

662
00:39:24,280 --> 00:39:24,900
Look at these trucks.

663
00:39:25,880 --> 00:39:26,260
See?

664
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,650
And our shiny new equipment.

665
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:32,130
Not just the coal preparation plant,

666
00:39:33,030 --> 00:39:34,170
we actually own a mine.

667
00:39:36,800 --> 00:39:37,210
A mine!

668
00:39:39,630 --> 00:39:40,090
Step over,

669
00:39:42,190 --> 00:39:42,690
leave all the old stuff behind.

670
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:58,090
Long,

671
00:39:59,190 --> 00:39:59,900
welcome home.

672
00:40:01,510 --> 00:40:01,940
Mr. Yu.

673
00:40:04,150 --> 00:40:04,610
Look at you,

674
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:06,380
you've lost weight.

675
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:07,210
I'm alright.

676
00:40:08,280 --> 00:40:09,460
You're our hero.

677
00:40:11,150 --> 00:40:11,570
What's wrong?

678
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,980
Getting emotional now?

679
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:16,980
That's okay.

680
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:17,940
Let it out if you need to.

681
00:40:18,710 --> 00:40:21,130
Things will get better from here,

682
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:22,010
and soon

683
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:23,570
you won't have anything to cry about.

684
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:26,170
Long,

685
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:26,820
look around.

686
00:40:27,360 --> 00:40:27,900
From now on,

687
00:40:28,840 --> 00:40:29,570
the whole

688
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:31,490
prep plant

689
00:40:32,510 --> 00:40:34,740
is yours to run.

690
00:40:35,070 --> 00:40:35,460
Sounds good?

691
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:36,570
Can you handle it?

692
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:06,210
You're back.

693
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:08,980
Haven't eaten yet, right?

694
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:12,530
Go wash up,

695
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:13,820
I'll make some noodles.

696
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:40,300
There, there.

697
00:41:41,070 --> 00:41:42,530
Wait on the couch,
dinner'll be ready soon.

698
00:41:54,550 --> 00:41:55,940
Why does nothing ever go my way?

699
00:41:56,630 --> 00:41:57,460
After three years,

700
00:41:58,230 --> 00:41:59,940
the Wan Hai case finally wraps up,

701
00:42:01,110 --> 00:42:03,260
I thought the mess with Wanchuan Mining

702
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,170
would finally be over—

703
00:42:04,800 --> 00:42:06,380
and then this disaster hits.

704
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:07,900
Who's going to

705
00:42:08,800 --> 00:42:09,900
take it on now?

706
00:42:10,510 --> 00:42:11,530
Give it time.

707
00:42:12,030 --> 00:42:12,940
I'm sure you can find someone.

708
00:42:15,070 --> 00:42:15,860
I wouldn't count on it.

709
00:42:19,070 --> 00:42:19,530
Well,

710
00:42:20,360 --> 00:42:21,130
any company that even considers this

711
00:42:22,840 --> 00:42:24,090
has to have real resources.

712
00:42:26,320 --> 00:42:27,210
So,

713
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:28,860
who's interested right now?

714
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:30,210
Tianlong Company.

715
00:42:36,190 --> 00:42:37,090
Tianlong?

716
00:42:38,320 --> 00:42:39,980
Run by Zijian's boss.

717
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,380
You've met him before.

718
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:43,940
What a shame.

719
00:42:49,320 --> 00:42:50,980
When did you guys start

720
00:42:52,510 --> 00:42:53,530
talking with Tianlong Company?

721
00:42:56,880 --> 00:42:57,570
Sure,

722
00:42:57,960 --> 00:42:58,980
I'm very interested.

723
00:42:59,510 --> 00:43:00,050
As long as we have you

724
00:43:00,070 --> 00:43:01,210
and the Development Zone
Managing Committee

725
00:43:01,230 --> 00:43:01,940
behind us,

726
00:43:02,800 --> 00:43:04,010
we're ready to make our contribution.

727
00:43:07,550 --> 00:43:09,260
I met up with the guy

728
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:11,900
after the Wan Hai trial started
and mentioned it to him.

729
00:43:12,630 --> 00:43:13,740
He was interested,

730
00:43:13,960 --> 00:43:14,610
looked eager to take it over.

731
00:43:18,550 --> 00:43:19,460
Work together?

732
00:43:20,190 --> 00:43:21,170
No.

733
00:43:21,920 --> 00:43:22,740
I buy either the whole mine or nothing.

734
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:25,050
That's my one condition.

735
00:43:26,070 --> 00:43:27,340
It has to be a 100% buyout,

736
00:43:28,670 --> 00:43:29,940
that's the only way
I'll put in everything I've got.

737
00:43:36,480 --> 00:43:37,010
What's wrong?

738
00:43:41,510 --> 00:43:42,690
The noodles are good,

739
00:43:45,280 --> 00:43:47,260
I just don't have an appetite right now.

740
00:44:18,520 --> 00:44:22,160
♪Had it not been for you♪

741
00:44:22,160 --> 00:44:25,920
♪I'd never have known how love feels♪

742
00:44:25,920 --> 00:44:31,160
♪The darker the night,
the brighter the stars shine♪

743
00:44:33,480 --> 00:44:37,120
♪If not for the words you let me hear♪

744
00:44:37,120 --> 00:44:40,880
♪How could I break from chains of fear♪

745
00:44:40,880 --> 00:44:46,840
♪To feel myself rise, then gently fall♪

746
00:44:48,640 --> 00:44:52,360
♪No rest, no peace, no dare♪

747
00:44:52,360 --> 00:45:00,440
♪No dreams, no thoughts,
no confusion or fear♪

748
00:45:03,600 --> 00:45:07,280
♪No fight, no cry, no words to lend♪

749
00:45:07,280 --> 00:45:12,760
♪I owed you nothing in the end♪

750
00:45:18,360 --> 00:45:21,920
♪But still, I thank you♪

751
00:45:21,920 --> 00:45:25,920
♪For blooming my midnights♪

752
00:45:25,920 --> 00:45:28,360
♪Even through roads both rough and wide♪

753
00:45:28,360 --> 00:45:33,280
♪You traced the shape of free inside♪

754
00:45:33,280 --> 00:45:37,040
♪Someone will always hold that grace♪

755
00:45:37,040 --> 00:45:40,760
♪A love that time cannot erase♪

756
00:45:40,760 --> 00:45:43,360
♪And what I once clung to
with all my might♪

757
00:45:43,360 --> 00:45:48,760
♪Now softly lands beyond the light♪

758
00:45:48,760 --> 00:45:52,400
♪No sleep, no rest, no will to try♪

759
00:45:52,400 --> 00:46:01,960
♪No dreams, no thoughts,
no confusion or fear♪

760
00:46:03,760 --> 00:46:07,360
♪No fight, no cry, no words to lend♪

761
00:46:07,360 --> 00:46:13,320
♪But love will bloom in me till the end♪
